    <line char="mother" changeDefAnim="grin">Well, it’s obvious!</line>
    <line char="mother" changeDefAnim="disgust">My perfect little boy has had his mind tainted by that... pest, filling your head with all kinds of shady thoughts.</line>
    <line char="pico" changeDefAnim="annoyed">You fucking whore.</line>
    <line char="pico" changeDefAnim="worry">All I’ve ever done is care for him.</line>
    <line char="pico" changeDefAnim="annoyed">That’s more than you or that monster you call a husband has ever done.</line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="uncomfortable">Pico!-</line>
    <line char="mother" changeDefAnim="snarl">Quiet! How dare you accuse my family of such things!</line>
    <line char="mother" changeDefAnim="grin">We love you so much Benjamin, why don’t you just come with me-</line>
    <line char="bf" changeDefAnim="concerned">I’m not going with you.</line>
    <line char="mother" changeDefAnim="stern" changeMusic="dio/music/cars" musicVolume="0.8">Hmph. Fine, be that way.</line>

